<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.9">
<l>kaṟpakak kāvu karutiya kātalik</l>
<l>kippoḻu tīvaṉeṉṟu vintiraṉ kāviṉil</l>
<l>niṟpaṉa ceytu nilāttikaḻ muṟṟattu</l>
<l>ḷuyttavaṉ eṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">umparkōṉ eṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying to [his] beloved</l>
<l rend="indent">who desired the grove of Kaṟpaka trees in Indra’s garden,</l>
<l>“I will give [it to you] now,”</l>
<l>[and] made it stand in [her] bright, moonlit courtyard,</l>
<l>he who carried [it] will embrace me from behind.</l>
<l>The King of celestials will embrace me from behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
